<p>&nbsp;</p>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
<ul>
<li>If a director is not in, slide the application pages under the door or leave it in the English Dept. Office, Rigby Hall 180. Your application is NOT complete until a director has received it. Applicants must be cleared for eligibility through the Dean of Student's office.</li>
<li>You'll receive an email notifying you about acceptance to the program.&nbsp;A $500 deposit is due two weeks after notification.</li>
<li>Students on any track may apply.</li>
</ul>
<p>&nbsp;</p>
